3c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe \u003cstrong\u003eGenkan\u003c/strong\u003e marks the entrance, with a bench that doubles as shoe storage – a must in Japan, where it’s customary to remove your shoes before entering – and a coat rack crafted from repurposed bottles. The \u003cem\u003eOfuro\u003c/em\u003e module, dedicated to hygiene and well-being, features a reinterpreted Shoji sliding partition and a traditional Japanese soaking bath.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"attachment_575569\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=575569\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-575569\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-11-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A small, modern wooden structure with large glass windows stands among trees; a bicycle with a basket is parked nearby\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-11-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-11-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-11-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-11-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-11.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-11-810x1215.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eOfuro module\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"attachment_575562\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=575562\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-575562\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-s