sign-milk.com/?attachment_id=575568\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-575568\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-10-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A small wooden reading nook with a bench, open book, shelves holding books and stationery, and a window showing greenery outside\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-10-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-10-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-10-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-10-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-10.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-10-810x1215.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eTatami module\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe \u003cstrong\u003eTatami\u003c/strong\u003e module offers a foldable sleeping area that maximizes every square inch. And outside, a \u003cstrong\u003eNiwa\u003c/strong\u003e garden nods to Japan’s courtyard gardens, offering a place to grow food, meditate, or simply stay still.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"attachment_575592\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=575592\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-575592\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-5-810x1215.jpeg\" alt=\"A small modern shed with wooden walls, a metal door, potted plants on shelves, steps, and an outdoor water feature with a white spout and bucket in a garden setting\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-5-810x1215.jpeg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-5-800x1200.jpeg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-5-768x1152.jpeg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-5-1024x1536.jpeg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-5.jpeg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-5-810x1215.jpeg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eNiwa module at left\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"attachment_575633\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=575633\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-575633\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-39-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-39-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-39-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-39-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-39-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-39.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-39-810x1215.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eHollow shelf, made from bamboo boxes\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIn the spirit of doing more with less, MUJI and Studio 5∙5 also introduced MUJI MUJI 5∙5, a collection of DIY creations that transform existing products into new objects for daily living. With just a few tweaks, familiar MUJI products turn into entirely new creations: a birdhouse built from a bookend and drawer, a hollow shelf fashioned from bamboo boxes, even a gong made from a measuring bowl and coffee spoon.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"attachment_575649\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=575649\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-575649\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-20-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A two-tiered plastic storage bin with wooden support, holding bottles in the lower bin and a glass on the upper tray, placed next to glassware and bowls on shelves\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-20-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-20-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-20-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-20-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-20.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-20-810x1215.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eTray cart, made from a pinewood board, wood tray, and storage box\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"attachment_575555\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=575555\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-575555\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003c