.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-25-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-25.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-25-810x1215.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eGong bowl, made from a measuring bowl, coffee spoon, suction cups, and aluminum hooks\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMore than a showcase of clever design, the Manifesto House and MUJI MUJI collection embody a shared belief between MUJI and Studio 5∙5: that true living isn’t about accumulating more, but about choosing well. Every object, every space, is a quiet affirmation of shaping a life with intention – focusing on what is essential, what is versatile, and what will truly endure. It’s proof that intentional design – and a little DIY creativity – can go a long way.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=575559\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-575559\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-7-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Outdoor wall with a wooden panel, grid section holding cleaning tools, a window with shelves visible inside, and plants in the foreground\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-7-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-7-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-7-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-7-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/muji-studio-5-5-manifesto-house-diy-series-7.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (ma